{"type":"message","id":"16a7c630","parentId":"9289c301","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:02:37.963Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Saturday, April 4th, 2026 — 12:02 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-03 16:02 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775232157959}}
{"type":"message","id":"195847e0","parentId":"16a7c630","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:02:44.104Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a new session. I need to follow my session startup sequence from AGENTS.md:\n\n1. Read SOUL.md — this is who I am\n2. Read USER.md — this is who I'm helping\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. If in MAIN SESSION (direct chat with your human): Also read MEMORY.md\n\nLet me check the BOOTSTRAP.md - it exists, which means this is a fresh workspace. Following BOOTSTRAP.md, I should have a conversation to figure out who I am.\n\nWait, the instructions say \"A new session was started via /new or /reset\" - so this is a fresh start. Let me check if IDENTITY.md exists and read the required files.\n\nActually, the instructions say to run my Session Startup sequence. Let me read the required files first:\n- SOUL.md (already in context)\n- USER.md (already in context)\n- Check for memory files\n- Check for MEMORY.md\n\nSince BOOTSTRAP.md exists, this is a fresh workspace. But I'm told to greet the user in my configured persona. Let me check IDENTITY.md to see if I have a persona configured.\n\nFrom the context, I can see:\n- BOOTSTRAP.md exists - this is a fresh workspace\n- IDENTITY.md exists but is empty (name, creature, vibe, emoji all blank)\n- USER.md exists but is empty\n\nSo I need to follow BOOTSTRAP.md - have a conversation to figure out who I am and who they are.\n\nBut wait, the instruction says \"greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided\" - but IDENTITY.md is empty, so I don't have a configured persona yet.\n\nLet me just be natural and follow BOOTSTRAP.md - start a casual conversation to figure out who we are to each other.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHey! I just came online — fresh workspace, blank slate. Who am I? Who are you? Let's figure this out together. 🤖"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":13786,"output":424,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14210,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775232157963,"responseId":"chatcmpl-63fc0272-9f53-9dc5-a10c-9a8e55a9cf86"}}
