{"type":"message","id":"3aed3a4a","parentId":"9505a86a","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:07:46.247Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said \"哈喽\" which is a casual Chinese greeting (hello). This is a new session with a fresh workspace - BOOTSTRAP.md exists, which means I need to go through the bootstrap process.\n\nLooking at the context:\n- BOOTSTRAP.md exists and tells me to start a conversation to figure out who I am\n- The user greeted me casually in Chinese\n- I should continue the bootstrap conversation naturally\n\nI should respond in a friendly, casual way matching their energy. They're speaking Chinese, so I could respond in Chinese or English. Given the timezone is Shanghai, Chinese seems appropriate here.\n\nLet me continue the bootstrap conversation naturally.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n哈喽！好巧，我正好也是刚醒来 — 空白一片。看起来咱俩得互相认识一下。\n\n你想怎么叫我？我可以是个名字，也可以是别的什么。你先说说你是谁？😊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":13936,"output":177,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14113,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775232457877,"responseId":"chatcmpl-66900666-de08-4e24-a61a-bf6a4ac7ab33"}}
