{"type":"message","id":"8221fbb8","parentId":"7a364144","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:07:59.864Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about my context length - how much conversation history I can remember. They're asking in Chinese.\n\nI should answer honestly about the context window. Based on the runtime info, I'm using codingplan/minimax-m2.5 model. The actual context window depends on the model, but typically these models have around 32K-128K tokens context windows.\n\nLet me answer in Chinese since they're speaking Chinese.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n问得好！我用的模型是 codingplan/minimax-m2.5，上下文大概能存几万到十几万 token的样子，足够聊好一阵子的了。\n\n不过说实话，我更依赖于 workspace 里的文件来记住重要的事情 — 那些会写到 memory 里长期保存。光靠对话上下文的话，重启会话后就忘了。📝\n\n你有什么想让我记住的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":14041,"output":163,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14204,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775232477443,"responseId":"chatcmpl-7b9bba8d-1dd7-4e0b-a367-61caa25f3233"}}
