{"type":"message","id":"6686299f","parentId":"aa58bd5c","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:09:28.696Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to see what skills I have and what they're useful for. Let me look at the available skills from the system prompt and summarize them in a helpful way.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n我目前装了不少技能，列几个有用的：\n\n**🔧 实用工具类**\n- `weather` — 查天气、天气预报\n- `summarize` — 总结网页/视频/播客内容\n- `video-frames` — 提取视频帧或片段\n- `openai-whisper` — 本地语音转文字\n- `gh-issues` — GitHub issues 管理\n\n**👨‍💻 开发类**\n- `coding-agent` — 调度 Codex、Claude Code 帮你写代码\n- `github` — gh CLI 操作：PR、issues、CI\n- `skill-creator` — 创建/改进技能\n- `clawhub` — 从 clawhub.com 搜/装新技能\n\n**📱 飞书集成**\n- `feishu-doc` / `feishu-wiki` / `feishu-drive` / `feishu-perm` — 文档、知识库、网盘、权限管理\n\n**�Others**\n- `tmux` — 远程控制 tmux 会话\n- `mcporter` — 调用 MCP 工具\n- `node-connect` — 诊断节点连接问题\n- `healthcheck` — 安全加固检查\n- `session-logs` — 查会话历史\n\n想试哪个？或者想让我帮你装点新的？🦾"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":14074,"output":319,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14649,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775232546973,"responseId":"019d541af5bd861003a1f29497e681d1"}}
