{"type":"message","id":"dd4b1d01","parentId":"1c29aae6","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:43:08.732Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"现在呢\" which means \"How about now?\" or \"What's happening now?\" in Chinese. They might be checking if I'm still there or asking about the current state.\n\nGiven the context - it's a new session, we just met, they've been asking questions about my capabilities and Claude Code - I should respond naturally. Maybe they're just checking in or wondering what I'm up to.\n\nI'll keep it casual and open-ended.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n还在呢，刚才处理了一个心跳检查，正好有空。\n\n咱俩刚才聊到一半 — 你想继续聊技能、让我帮你做点啥，还是继续互相了解？😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":14738,"output":126,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14864,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775234586779,"responseId":"chatcmpl-f99f05bc-57d0-4571-be46-048b0e4ec705"}}
