{"type":"message","id":"e74b9db1","parentId":"a610a519","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:44:34.452Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, so Feishu is enabled and there's a direct session with Feishu that was active 6 minutes ago. The channel is ON and OK. Let me check the logs to see if there were any errors when the user tried to communicate.\n\nWait, looking at the session list, there's already a Feishu direct session that was active 6 minutes ago. So communication should be working...\n\nThe user might be asking why they can't communicate via Feishu *right now*. Let me check if there are any issues in the recent logs or if the session is still active.\n\nActually, I should ask the user for more context - what exactly happens when they try to message via Feishu? Any error messages? Or just no response?\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n从状态看 Feishu 通道是开启的，而且刚才 6 分钟前还有个飞书对话在活跃。\n\n但你说不能跟我沟通了 — 具体是啥情况？\n- 发送消息没反应？\n- 报错提示？\n- 还是机器人根本没回？\n\n可以帮我看下报错信息或者日志吗？📋"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":20571,"output":219,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20790,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775234670277,"responseId":"chatcmpl-63fd961a-afab-4211-afcc-46dff4db2f09"}}
