{"type":"message","id":"d5ccd95a","parentId":"5db9752b","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:44:59.931Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user just sent an empty message (the metadata block but no actual text). This seems like they might be waiting for me to continue, or perhaps there was an issue with their message. \n\nI should wait briefly or acknowledge that I received something but need more info.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n收到你发了消息，但看起来是空的 😅\n\n想继续的话随时说 — 是遇到啥具体问题了吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":5783,"output":79,"cacheRead":14848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20710,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775234691997,"responseId":"019d543bae727decbf79207ff54f4300"}}
