{"type":"message","id":"2c019b27","parentId":"3f7ca805","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:45:46.810Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从日志看，最后一条飞书消息是 00:38 用户说\"现在你可以调用Claude Code了吧\"，然后 dispatching 了。但我没有看到 \"dispatch complete\" 的日志。\n\n让我检查是否有更多的日志，看看是否有 dispatch 失败或错误。\n\n用户说飞书不回他了 - 可能是：\n1. 飞书消息没到达服务器\n2. 服务器处理了但没回复成功\n\n让我再查一下，看看有什么更多信息。也需要检查飞书通道配置。\n\n从 status 看，Feishu 显示 OK，没报错。但可能配置有问题。\n\n问题是 00:38 那条 \"现在你可以调用Claude Code了吧\" 后，我应该回复了，但用户说没收到。\n\n让我用 openclaw status --deep 检查飞书详细状态，以及看看最近是否有什么错误。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d543bcebe4451d29188f115c3dba6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"tail -50 /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-04-04.log | grep -i \"error\\|fail\\|reject\" | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":15300,"output":211,"cacheRead":20608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36119,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775234734900,"responseId":"019d543ba6b9844f6b2504c46967e7f3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"995d2f18","parentId":"2c019b27","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:45:46.826Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d543bcebe4451d29188f115c3dba6","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"0\":\"{\\\"subsystem\\\":\\\"gateway/channels/feishu\\\"}\",\"1\":\"feishu: streaming start failed: Error: Create card request failed with HTTP 400\",\"_meta\":{\"runtime\":\"node\",\"runtimeVersion\":\"22.22.1\",\"hostname\":\"unknown\",\"name\":\"{\\\"subsystem\\\":\\\"gateway/channels/feishu\\\"}\",\"parentNames\":[\"openclaw\"],\"date\":\"2026-04-03T16:16:20.808Z\",\"logLevelId\":5,\"logLevelName\":\"ERROR\",\"path\":{\"fullFilePath\":\"file:///home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js:454:14\",\"fileName\":\"subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js\",\"fileNameWithLine\":\"subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js:454\",\"fileColumn\":\"14\",\"fileLine\":\"454\",\"filePath\":\".nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js\",\"filePathWithLine\":\".nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js:454\",\"method\":\"logToFile\"}},\"time\":\"2026-04-04T00:16:20.808+08:00\"}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9,"aggregated":"{\"0\":\"{\\\"subsystem\\\":\\\"gateway/channels/feishu\\\"}\",\"1\":\"feishu: streaming start failed: Error: Create card request failed with HTTP 400\",\"_meta\":{\"runtime\":\"node\",\"runtimeVersion\":\"22.22.1\",\"hostname\":\"unknown\",\"name\":\"{\\\"subsystem\\\":\\\"gateway/channels/feishu\\\"}\",\"parentNames\":[\"openclaw\"],\"date\":\"2026-04-03T16:16:20.808Z\",\"logLevelId\":5,\"logLevelName\":\"ERROR\",\"path\":{\"fullFilePath\":\"file:///home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js:454:14\",\"fileName\":\"subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js\",\"fileNameWithLine\":\"subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js:454\",\"fileColumn\":\"14\",\"fileLine\":\"454\",\"filePath\":\".nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/l