{"type":"message","id":"0b2fe92c","parentId":"90f495a5","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:48:42.686Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Feishu health is \"OK\". But the user's messages aren't reaching the gateway. Let me check if there's a webhook or websocket issue. Actually, wait - the connectionMode is \"websocket\", which should maintain a persistent connection. Let me check when the websocket was last connected, or if there's any recent error.\n\nActually, one thing I notice is that the last feishu message in logs is from 00:38:23, and it's 00:48 now. That's 10 minutes. The user might be sending messages that aren't getting logged because maybe they're not reaching openclaw at all.\n\nLet me check if there's a websocket connection issue or if the server was restarted recently.\n\nActually wait - the user is asking why feishu doesn't respond. From the logs, I see:\n1. The last message received was at 00:38:23 (\"现在你可以调用Claude Code了吧\")\n2. That message was dispatched successfully (`dispatching to agent`)\n3. The dispatch was complete (`dispatch complete (queuedFinal=true, replies=?)`)\n\nSo the conversation was working up until 00:38. After that, nothing in the logs.\n\nLet me check if there's a recent error or if the gateway has been restarted.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8de301c7521441d9ae1b93f1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"tail -20 /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-04-04.log"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":47756,"output":290,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48046,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775234917285,"responseId":"chatcmpl-57fce241-1100-4596-9ba9-7bbbbd0df8cc"}}
