{"type":"message","id":"0e75a90d","parentId":"155faa4e","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:48:49.197Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see recent log activity from 00:48 (when the user was checking status), but no Feishu messages being received. \n\nWait, actually I just realized - maybe the user is sending messages but they're not even reaching the gateway. Or maybe they're sending through the Control UI (which is what they're using now), not through Feishu.\n\nLooking at this more carefully - the user is asking why Feishu doesn't respond. But they're currently chatting with me through the Control UI (webchat). So maybe they sent a message through Feishu and I didn't respond?\n\nLet me check the most recent log entries to see if there's any new feishu messages. Actually the last log line I see is from 00:48:36 and that's just plugin registration, not any Feishu messages. Let me see if maybe there's a connection issue - the WebSocket might have dropped.\n\nActually wait - looking back at the config, it says `connectionMode: \"websocket\"`. This means OpenClaw connects to Feishu's WebSocket server to receive messages. Maybe that connection dropped.\n\nLet me restart the gateway to see if that helps, or check the websocket status. Actually, I think the best approach is to just restart the gateway to re-establish the connection.\n\nActually wait - let me think about this more. The user says it was working before. The last message was 10 minutes ago. The logs show no new messages from Feishu after 00:38. This could be:\n1. WebSocket connection dropped and didn't reconnect\n2. Feishu App token expired\n3. Something changed on Feishu's side\n\nLet me restart the gateway to see if that helps.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n日志显示 00:38 后就没有收到任何飞书消息了，但网关显示 Feishu 状态是 OK。\n\n可能是 WebSocket 连接断开了。试试重启网关：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e359ad3c9e3047f0bd62bb5b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw gateway restart"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":53687,"output":422,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54109,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775234922705,"responseId":"chatcmpl-e240de7b-ff86-4dbf-9d20-0757541f6240"}}
