{"type":"message","id":"bf6ff124","parentId":"15b2567a","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:55:19.015Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The log clearly shows:\n\n1. Gateway was restarted at 00:48:51 (the \"abort signal received\" log)\n2. Gateway reconnected at 00:48:58\n3. Feishu messages came in:\n   - 00:49:27: \"哈喽\" - replied (replies=1)\n   - 00:49:47: \"现在你可以调用Claude Code了吧\" - replied (replies=2)\n   - 00:50:38: \"可以用它帮我审查修bug吗\" - dispatched to agent\n\n4. Then the typing indicator stopped at 00:53:25 (2 minutes after the last message)\n\nSo it looks like the last message at 00:50:38 was dispatched to the agent but I don't see a \"dispatch complete\" log after that. This could mean:\n- The agent is still processing\n- Or there was an issue\n\nLet me check if there's more recent activity or errors. The gateway seems to be working fine - it's receiving and dispatching messages. The problem might be that the last message is still being processed or the reply failed.\n\nActually, looking at this again - the last message at 00:50:38 (\"可以用它帮我审查修bug吗\") shows \"dispatching to agent\" but no \"dispatch complete\" in the log. That suggests the agent might have crashed or gotten stuck.\n\nBut wait - the user is now chatting with me via webchat, which means the gateway is still running. So it's not a complete crash. Maybe the agent is just slow.\n\nLet me tell the user what I found.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到问题了！日志显示：\n\n**✅ 网关已恢复**\n- 00:48:51 网关重启\n- 00:48:58 飞书 WebSocket 重连成功\n- 收到并处理了消息：\n  - 00:49:27 \"哈喽\" → 回复成功\n  - 00:49:47 \"现在你可以调用Claude Code了吧\" → 回复成功\n  - 00:50:38 \"可以用它帮我审查修bug吗\" → 已分发给 Agent\n\n**⚠️ 问题**：最后一条消息（00:50:38）分发给 Agent 后，日志显示 \"dispatching to agent\" 但没有显示 \"dispatch complete\"。\n\n这意味着 Agent 可能卡住了或者回复发送失败。你在飞书那边收到这条消息的回复了吗？\n\n现在网关是正常工作的，你可以再试一条消息测试一下。🚀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":79957,"output":5