{"type":"message","id":"ba303b1d","parentId":"3d91fc53","timestamp":"2026-04-03T17:05:58.475Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d544e7a945bc82e5116ee1a65dd72","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:    Usually no. OpenClaw needs large context + strong safety; small cards truncate and leak. If you must, run the **largest** MiniMax M2.5 build you can locally (LM Studio) and see [/gateway/local-models](/gateway/local-models). Smaller/quantized models increase prompt-injection risk - see [Security](/gateway/security).\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/providers/bedrock.md:- Reasoning support depends on the model; check the Bedrock model card for\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/tools/index.md:- `send`（文本 + 可选媒体；MS Teams 还支持用于 Adaptive Cards 的 `card`）\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/feishu.md:      \"cardkit:card:read\",\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/feishu.md:      \"cardkit:card:write\",\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/msteams.md:`card` 参数接受 Adaptive Card JSON 对象。当提供 `card` 时，消息文本是可选的。\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/msteams.md:  \"card\": {\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/msteams.md:  --card '{\"type\":\"AdaptiveCard\",\"version\":\"1.5\",\"body\":[{\"type\":\"TextBlock\",\"text\":\"Hello!\"}]}'\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/msteams.md:参见 [Adaptive Cards 文档](https://adaptivecards.io/)了解卡片模式和示例。目标格式详情见下方[目标格式](#target-formats)。\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/msteams.md:  --card '{\"type\":\"AdaptiveCard\",\"version\":\"1.5\",\"body\":[{\"type\":\"TextBlock\",\"text\":\"Hello\"}]}'\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/msteams.md:  \"card\": {\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/line.md:        altText: \"Status card\",\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/line.md:LINE 插件还提供 `/card` 命令用于 Flex 消息预设：\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/line.md:/card info \"Welcome\" \"Thanks for joining!\"\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/diagnostics/flags.md:- Wildcards are supported:\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/date-time.md:card includes a timestamp line.\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/install/raspberry-pi.md:- MicroSD card (16 GB+) or USB SSD (better performance)\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/install/raspberry-pi.md:    4. Flash to your SD card or USB drive, insert it, and boot the Pi.\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/install/raspberry-pi.md:**Use a USB SSD** -- SD cards are slow and wear out. A USB SSD dramatically improves performance. See the [Pi USB boot guide](https://www.raspberrypi.com/documentation/computers/raspberry-pi.html#usb-mass-storage-boot).\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/install/raspberry-pi.md:**Slow performance** -- Use a USB SSD instead of an SD card. Check for CPU throttling with `vcgencmd get_throttled` (should return `0x0`)."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":72,"aggregated":"/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:    Usually no. OpenClaw needs large context + strong safety; small cards truncate and leak. If you must, run the **largest** MiniMax M2.5 build you can locally (LM Studio) and see [/gateway/loca