{"type":"message","id":"dc214272","parentId":"17df25b7","timestamp":"2026-04-03T17:06:17.818Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d544e93a30502fbeb5bd73d467147","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"model: gpt-5.4\n      \"application:application.app_message_stats.overview:readonly\",\n      \"im:message\",\n      \"im:message.group_at_msg:readonly\",\n      \"im:message.p2p_msg:readonly\",\n      \"im:message:readonly\",\n      \"im:message:send_as_bot\",\n2. 添加事件：`im.message.receive_v1`\n如果你使用 `connectionMode: \"webhook\"`，请同时设置 `verificationToken` 和 `encryptKey`。飞书 webhook 服务器默认绑定到 `127.0.0.1`；只有在你明确需要不同绑定地址时，才设置 `webhookHost`。\n- `resolveSenderNames`（默认 `true`）：设为 `false` 时，跳过发送者资料查询调用。\n      resolveSenderNames: false,\n          resolveSenderNames: false,\n| `/model`  | 显示/切换模型  |\n2. 确保事件订阅包含 `im.message.receive_v1`\n1. 确保应用具有 `im:message:send_as_bot` 权限\n- `textChunkLimit`：出站文本分块大小（默认：2000 个字符）\n            mode: \"persistent\",\n```text\n| `channels.feishu.connectionMode`                  | 事件传输模式                     | `websocket`      |\n| `channels.feishu.textChunkLimit`                  | 消息分块大小                     | `2000`           |"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9,"aggregated":"model: gpt-5.4\n      \"application:application.app_message_stats.overview:readonly\",\n      \"im:message\",\n      \"im:message.group_at_msg:readonly\",\n      \"im:message.p2p_msg:readonly\",\n      \"im:message:readonly\",\n      \"im:message:send_as_bot\",\n2. 添加事件：`im.message.receive_v1`\n如果你使用 `connectionMode: \"webhook\"`，请同时设置 `verificationToken` 和 `encryptKey`。飞书 webhook 服务器默认绑定到 `127.0.0.1`；只有在你明确需要不同绑定地址时，才设置 `webhookHost`。\n- `resolveSenderNames`（默认 `true`）：设为 `false` 时，跳过发送者资料查询调用。\n      resolveSenderNames: false,\n          resolveSenderNames: false,\n| `/model`  | 显示/切换模型  |\n2. 确保事件订阅包含 `im.message.receive_v1`\n1. 确保应用具有 `im:message:send_as_bot` 权限\n- `textChunkLimit`：出站文本分块大小（默认：2000 个字符）\n            