{"type":"message","id":"6d9453ab","parentId":"5fda246a","timestamp":"2026-04-03T17:06:55.155Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue. The streaming response is trying to create a card (interactive card) to reply with, but it's failing with HTTP 400. This could be because:\n\n1. The Feishu app doesn't have the `cardkit:card:write` permission\n2. The card creation API is rejecting the request for some reason\n\nLet me check what permissions the Feishu app needs. But first, let me see if there's an option in configuration to use text messages instead of cards.\n\nActually, let me try a different approach. Let me check if there's a way to configure the message mode - maybe using text instead of interactive cards.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n问题找到了！OpenClaw 使用 **卡片消息 (interactive card)** 来流式输出回复，但飞书 API 返回 400 错误。\n\n这说明你的飞书应用可能缺少卡片权限，或者配置有问题。\n\n让我检查一下需要的权限：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d544f3c424f02f82fff9940ec5935","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -i \"cardkit\\|permission\\|scope\" ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/feishu.md 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":4939,"output":250,"cacheRead":87936,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93125,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775236002552,"responseId":"019d544f1579120390b74d183c37a238"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b435e2cf","parentId":"6d9453ab","timestamp":"2026-04-03T17:06:55.178Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d544f3c424f02f82fff9940ec5935","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"在 **Permissions** 中，点击 **Batch import** 并粘贴：\n  \"scopes\": {\n      \"cardkit:card:read\",\n      \"cardkit:card:write\",\n![Configure permissions](../images/feishu-step4-permissions.png)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":10,"aggregated":"在 **Permissions** 中，点击 **Batch import** 并粘贴：\n  \"scopes\": {\n      \"cardkit:card:read\",\n      \"cardkit:card:write\",\n![Configure permissions](../images/feishu-step4-permissions.png)","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775236015175}}
{"type":"message","id":"59b7c6bb","parentId":"b435e2cf","timestamp":"2026-04-03T17:06:58.971Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the Feishu app needs `cardkit:card:write` permission to create cards. The user said they have the permissions enabled, but maybe there's an issue with the card creation itself.Let me also check if there's an alternative - maybe using text messages instead of cards. Let me look at the error more closely - it could be the card creation that's failing (first step) rather than the send.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n需要 **cardkit:card:write** 权限来创建卡片消息。你说已经开了权限，那可能是其他问题。\n\n有两个选择：\n\n**方案 1**：确认飞书后台权限\n- 去飞书开放平台 → 你的应用 → 权限管理\n- 确认已开通 `cardkit:card:write` 权限\n- 如果已开通，尝试重新发布应用版本\n\n**方案 2**：临时禁用卡片消息\n- 我可以帮你改配置，暂时用纯文本回复\n\n你想先试哪个？或者如果你能告诉我你在飞书开发者后台的具体权限截图，我可以帮你分析。🔧"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":93129,"output":212,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93341,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775236015178,"responseId":"chatcmpl-08309e33-cf46-4844-804a-d0285600e3d0"}}
