{"type":"message","id":"2dd48765","parentId":"aa961c23","timestamp":"2026-04-03T17:10:30.801Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user just enabled the cardkit permissions. Let me test if it works now by having them send a message through Feishu again. But first, I should check if the gateway needs to be restarted for the permission changes to take effect.\n\nActually, the permissions are based on the app's credentials, not the running gateway process. The gateway should pick up the new permissions automatically when making API calls. Let me have them test again.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n太好了！现在权限应该生效了。试试再给我发条消息？\n\n我这边也会盯着日志，看卡片消息能不能成功发送。🚀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":92859,"output":118,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92977,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775236227669,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9c58fbac-5983-458f-b566-0b9faefe9457"}}
